  "title": "The excellence of asking for Allah's blessings upon the Prophet PBUH",
  "source": "Hisn al-Muslim 221",
  "arabic": "وَقَالَ صلى الله عليه وسلم الْبَخِيلُ مَنْ ذُكِرْتُ عِنْدَهُ فَلَمْ يُصَلِّ عَلَيَّ",
  "meaning": "He (PBUH) also said: ‘A miser is one whom when I am mentioned to him, fails to send prayers upon me.",
